MenuItems.Description:
A selection of finger sandwiches, pastries and scones. Finger sandwiches include Cucumber, Egg & Truffle Mayonnaise, H. Foreman's Smoked Salmon, Salt Beef & Turnip, Turkey & Roasted Carrot Purée.
Pastries include Rocher, Pineapple, Bergamot & Lime, Mango Tart, Coffee & Lemongrass
Plain & Wholemeal Raisin Scones with jams. (Please note that tea will not be served)

Notes:
An eclectic, imaginative menu draws on Chef Jean-Georges Vongerichten's love of the city
and his experiences in the Far East.
Beloved British and Connaught classics stand alongside South-east Asian flavours, crafted from
fresh-from-the-market ingredients and farm-to-table produce.
